      "title_zh": "研究人员披露 WordPress 远程代码执行漏洞，利用 GPT 辅助发现且 PoC 已在网络流传",
      "title_orig": "RT Patrik Grobshäuser: Today we are releasing the blogpost for @hash_kitten amazing research that ruined all of our weekends. https://slcyber.io/rese...",
